# HCP Proposals

This directory contains design proposals for the evolution of the Humanitarian Connection Protocol (HCP).

Every significant change to the protocol should begin as a proposal.

The proposal process exists to encourage discussion, documentation and long-term consistency before implementation.

A proposal typically progresses through the following stages:

Draft

↓

Discussion

↓

Accepted

↓

Implemented

↓

Included in the HCP Specification

Not every proposal will be accepted.

The HCP Specification remains the authoritative definition of the protocol.
